                <h4>快速介绍</h4><p>中秋假期之后紧接着就要到十一假期！窝在家的时候来看看这周有什么好游戏吧！</p><p>本周内上架的游戏有<a href="https://store.steampowered.com/app/790820/Valkyria_Chronicles_4/" rel="noopener noreferrer" target="_blank">《战场女武神4》</a>、桌游 RPG<a href="https://store.steampowered.com/app/640820/Pathfinder_Kingmaker/" rel="noopener noreferrer" target="_blank">《开拓者：拥王者（Pathfinder: Kingmaker）》</a>的 PC 版，<a href="https://store.steampowered.com/app/658700/VRally_4_Day_One_Edition/" rel="noopener noreferrer" target="_blank">《真实赛车4》</a>、免费动作游戏《LET IT DIE》PC 版、《战争仪式》大逃杀模式<a href="https://store.steampowered.com/app/879160/Battlerite_Royale/" rel="noopener noreferrer" target="_blank">《Battlerite Royale》</a>、末日生存游戏<a href="https://store.steampowered.com/app/783170/INSOMNIA_The_Ark/" rel="noopener noreferrer" target="_blank">《失眠：方舟（INSOMNIA: The Ark）》</a>、双人欢乐合作游戏<a href="https://store.steampowered.com/app/904170/Never_Breakup/" rel="noopener noreferrer" target="_blank">《Never Breakup》</a>、国人恐怖解密 RPG<a href="https://store.steampowered.com/app/938810/__You_are_my_sanctuary/" rel="noopener noreferrer" target="_blank">《雨鸦》</a>。</p><h4>Life is Strange 2</h4><p>关键词：选择取向、剧情</p><p>发售日期：9月28日</p><p>奇异人生2的第一章来啦！！以下摘自剧情介绍：</p><blockquote><p>16岁的肖恩·迪亚兹与9岁的丹尼尔·迪亚兹两兄弟在西雅图遭遇了一场悲剧之后，不得不从家中逃离。为了躲避警察，二人动身前往墨西哥，同时还要尽力隐藏一种突然爆发的神秘特异功能。一路上，生活十分艰苦。如今肖恩必须完全担负起照顾年幼弟弟的责任，他开始意识到，他的决定将会永远改变他们的生活……</p></blockquote><p><img src="https://hive.indienova.com/farm/article/picture/2018/9/Life is Strange 2-1.jpg" class="fr-fic fr-dib" data-id="9687" data-result="success" class="aligncenter"></p><p><img src="https://hive.indienova.com/farm/article/picture/2018/9/Life is Strange 2-2.jpg" class="fr-fic fr-dib" data-id="9688" data-result="success" class="aligncenter"></p><p><img src="https://hive.indienova.com/farm/article/picture/2018/9/Life is Strange 2-3.jpg" class="fr-fic fr-dib" data-id="9689" data-result="success" class="aligncenter"></p><p class="hidden-xs"><iframe src="https://store.steampowered.com/widget/532210/" frameborder="0" style="width: 100%; height: 220px;"></iframe><br></p><h4>Broken Reality</h4><p>关键词：步行模拟、网络</p><p>发售日期：9月27日</p><p>我们曾经在<a href="https://indienova.com/indie-game-news/your-life-inside-a-browser/" rel="noopener noreferrer" target="_blank">《当你的人生被塞进了一款浏览器》</a>这篇文章中介绍过这款游戏。</p><p>在未来，超级公司 NATEM 掌握了绝大部分的数字服务的控制权，包括平民老百姓的电脑和互联网都受控于 NATEM。NATEM 将我们2D 的电脑屏幕界限破除，现在你的周身环境便是网站浏览器了。</p><p><img src="https://hive.indienova.com/farm/article/picture/2018/9/Broken Reality2.jpg" class="fr-fic fr-dib" data-id="9692" data-result="success" class="aligncenter"></p><p><img src="https://hive.indienova.com/farm/article/picture/2018/9/Broken Reality1.jpg" class="fr-fic fr-dib" data-id="9693" data-result="success" class="aligncenter"></p><p><img src="https://hive.indienova.com/farm/article/picture/2018/9/Broken Reality3.jpg" class="fr-fic fr-dib" data-id="9694" data-result="success" class="aligncenter"></p><p class="hidden-xs"><iframe src="https://store.steampowered.com/widget/757480/" frameborder="0" style="width: 100%; height: 220px;"></iframe><br></p><h4>侠隐行录：困境疑云 - Wuxia archive: Crisis escape</h4><p>关键词：武侠、解谜、脱出</p><p>发售日期：9月26日</p><p>主人公醒来后发现自己与多名侠客被困于未知地牢中，看似团结一致，实则每个人背后各有心思。侠客们是否能一起安全地逃离呢？幕后凶手究竟是？</p><p><img src="https://hive.indienova.com/farm/article/picture/2018/9/1-5.jpg" class="fr-fic fr-dib" data-id="9695" data-result="success" class="aligncenter"></p><p><img src="https://hive.indienova.com/farm/article/picture/2018/9/2-4.jpg" class="fr-fic fr-dib" data-id="9696" data-result="success" class="aligncenter"></p><p><img src="https://hive.indienova.com/farm/article/picture/2018/9/3-3.jpg" class="fr-fic fr-dib" data-id="9697" data-result="success" class="aligncenter"></p><p class="hidden-xs"><iframe src="https://store.steampowered.com/widget/923840/" frameborder="0" style="width: 100%; height: 220px;"></iframe><br></p><h4>Path to Mnemosyne</h4><p>关键词：解谜</p><p>发售日期：9月27日</p><p>这是一款由数十个谜题构成的催眠冒险游戏，在解开谜题的过程中，主角失去的记忆也会一一铺展开来。游戏支持中文。</p><p><img src="https://hive.indienova.com/farm/article/picture/2018/9/Path to Mnemosyne1.jpg" class="fr-fic fr-dib" data-id="9699" data-result="success" class="aligncenter"></p><p><img src="https://hive.indienova.com/farm/article/picture/2018/9/Path to Mnemosyne2.jpg" class="fr-fic fr-dib" data-id="9700" data-result="success" class="aligncenter"></p><p><img src="https://hive.indienova.com/farm/article/picture/2018/9/Path to Mnemosyne3.jpg" class="fr-fic fr-dib" data-id="9701" data-result="success" class="aligncenter"></p><p class="hidden-xs"><iframe src="https://store.steampowered.com/widget/770410/" frameborder="0" style="width: 100%; height: 220px;"></iframe><br></p><h4>Little Bug</h4><p>关键词：平台、解谜、假3D</p><p>发售日期：9月25日</p><p>小女孩 Nyah 在回家路上突然闯进了异世界，扮演引导她的光芒，解开谜题，回到原本的世界。</p><p><img src="https://hive.indienova.com/farm/article/picture/2018/9/Little Bug1.jpg" class="fr-fic fr-dib" data-id="9702" data-result="success" class="aligncenter"></p><p><img src="https://hive.indienova.com/farm/article/picture/2018/9/Little Bug2.jpg" class="fr-fic fr-dib" data-id="9703" data-result="success" class="aligncenter"></p><p><img src="https://hive.indienova.com/farm/article/picture/2018/9/Little Bug3.jpg" class="fr-fic fr-dib" data-id="9704" data-result="success" class="aligncenter"></p><p class="hidden-xs"><iframe src="https://store.steampowered.com/widget/822190/" frameborder="0" style="width: 100%; height: 220px;"></iframe><br></p><h4>Johnny Rocket</h4><p>关键词：漫画、平台动作</p><p>发售日期：9月27日</p><p>消灭邪恶的敌人！在幽默与漫画风格中打败 boss，了解主角 Johnny Rocket 的奇妙冒险。</p><p><img src="https://hive.indienova.com/farm/article/picture/2018/9/Johnny Rocket.gif" class="fr-fic fr-dib" data-id="9698" data-result="success" class="aligncenter"></p><p class="hidden-xs"><iframe src="https://store.steampowered.com/widget/942300/" frameborder="0" style="width: 100%; height: 220px;"></iframe><br></p><h4>The Last Train</h4><p>关键词：策略、模拟</p><p>发售日期：大概是9月27日</p><p>暂无中文。你是为数不多的二战后幸存者，运用你的火车驾驶技术来帮助他人吧！但是资源和能力总是有限的，有时候不得不面临道德的抉择……</p><p><img src="https://hive.indienova.com/farm/article/picture/2018/9/The Last Train1.jpg" class="fr-fic fr-dib" data-id="9705" data-result="success" class="aligncenter"></p><p><img src="https://hive.indienova.com/farm/article/picture/2018/9/The Last Train2.jpg" class="fr-fic fr-dib" data-id="9706" data-result="success" class="aligncenter"></p><p><img src="https://hive.indienova.com/farm/article/picture/2018/9/The Last Train3.jpg" class="fr-fic fr-dib" data-id="9707" data-result="success" style="width: 100%;" class="aligncenter"></p><p class="hidden-xs"><iframe src="https://store.steampowered.com/widget/858170/" frameborder="0" style="width: 100%; height: 220px;"></iframe><br></p><h4>Parkasaurus</h4><p>关键词：模拟、恐龙</p><p>发售日期：9月26日</p><p>建造你自己的恐龙公园！为每个种类的恐龙打造适合它们生存的生物圈，让你的游客在公园中获得最大的快乐。不过恐龙们可不是安分的动物，记得为恐龙逃跑和天气灾害做好应急措施！经营你的公园，同时回到过去寻找最古老的恐龙蛋吧！可以去<a href="https://weibo.com/p/1005056413444786" rel="noopener noreferrer" target="_blank">开发者的微博</a>看看。</p><p><img src="https://hive.indienova.com/farm/article/picture/2018/9/Parkasaurus mini.gif" class="fr-fic fr-dib" data-id="9678" data-result="success" class="aligncenter"></p><p><img src="https://hive.indienova.com/farm/article/picture/2018/9/Parkasaurus1.jpg" class="fr-fic fr-dib" data-id="9679" data-result="success" class="aligncenter"></p><p><img src="https://hive.indienova.com/farm/article/picture/2018/9/Parkasaurus3.png" class="fr-fic fr-dib" data-id="9680" data-result="success" class="aligncenter"></p><p class="hidden-xs"><iframe src="https://store.steampowered.com/widget/591460/" frameborder="0" style="width: 100%; height: 220px;"></iframe></p><h4>Timespinner</h4><p>关键词：平台动作、冒险</p><p>发售日期：9月26日</p><p>主人公 Lunais 为了给家人报仇，穿越时空，目的就是摧毁杀害了她家人的帝国。Lunais 可以停止时间，利用停止的敌人当作垫脚石来到达看似无法到达的地点，来解开谜题。同时也可以在时空中穿梭，在其它时代到达目前到达不了的地方。</p><p><img src="https://hive.indienova.com/farm/article/picture/2018/9/Timespinner1.jpg" class="fr-fic fr-dib" data-id="9681" data-result="success" class="aligncenter"></p><p><img src="https://hive.indienova.com/farm/article/picture/2018/9/Timespinner2.jpg" class="fr-fic fr-dib" data-id="9682" data-result="success" class="aligncenter"></p><p><img src="https://hive.indienova.com/farm/article/picture/2018/9/Timespinner3.jpg" class="fr-fic fr-dib" data-id="9683" data-result="success" class="aligncenter"></p><p class="hidden-xs"><iframe src="https://store.steampowered.com/widget/368620/" frameborder="0" style="width: 100%; height: 220px;"></iframe><br></p><h4>审判日 Big Day</h4><p>关键词：僵尸、血腥、射击</p><p>发售日期：9月25日</p><p>本游戏由站内会员@<a href="https://indienova.com/u/sonicshield" rel="noopener noreferrer" target="_blank">声波盾工作室</a>开发。病毒侵袭后的混沌社会，农场主潘乔穿梭在沦陷的世界中，尝试逃离一个个被雪毒疫情感染的城市，寻找失散的女儿 Liz，不想却被牵扯进国际阴谋，为了女儿的未来，潘乔不得不在秘密与诡计中前行，探寻僵尸危机的真相与救赎。</p><p><img src="https://hive.indienova.com/farm/article/picture/2018/9/Big Day1.jpg" class="fr-fic fr-dib" data-id="9684" data-result="success" class="aligncenter"></p><p><img src="https://hive.indienova.com/farm/article/picture/2018/9/Big Day2.jpg" class="fr-fic fr-dib" data-id="9685" data-result="success" class="aligncenter"></p><p><img src="https://hive.indienova.com/farm/article/picture/2018/9/Big Day3.jpg" class="fr-fic fr-dib" data-id="9686" data-result="success" class="aligncenter"></p><p class="hidden-xs"><iframe src="https://store.steampowered.com/widget/757630/" frameborder="0" style="width: 100%; height: 220px;"></iframe></p><h4>Depth of Extinction</h4><p>关键词：策略、科幻、永久死亡</p><p>发售日期：9月28日</p><p>暂无中文。世界充斥着暴力，作为人类最后一个政府的捍卫者，组建最棒的团队，击退未知的敌人！10种职业150+种武器可供选择，享受随机场景下的剧情吧！</p><p><img src="https://hive.indienova.com/farm/article/picture/2018/9/Depth of Extinction1.jpg" class="fr-fic fr-dib" data-id="9708" data-result="success" class="aligncenter"></p><p><img src="https://hive.indienova.com/farm/article/picture/2018/9/Depth of Extinction2.jpg" class="fr-fic fr-dib" data-id="9709" data-result="success" class="aligncenter"></p><p><img src="https://hive.indienova.com/farm/article/picture/2018/9/Depth of Extinction3.jpg" class="fr-fic fr-dib" data-id="9710" data-result="success" class="aligncenter"></p><p class="hidden-xs"><iframe src="https://store.steampowered.com/widget/636320/" frameborder="0" style="width: 100%; height: 220px;"></iframe><br></p><h4>Resynth</h4><p>关键词：音乐、解谜、关卡编辑</p><p>发售日期：9月28日</p><p>支持中文。一款音乐拼图游戏，拆解音乐的不同部分，利用碎片音效还原曲目。</p><p><img src="https://hive.indienova.com/farm/article/picture/2018/9/Resynth.gif" class="fr-fic fr-dib" data-id="9711" data-result="success" class="aligncenter"></p><p class="hidden-xs"><iframe src="https://store.steampowered.com/widget/819960/" frameborder="0" style="width: 100%; height: 220px;"></iframe><br></p><h4>Undelivered</h4><p>关键词：视觉小说、策略、侦探</p><p>发售日期：8月28日</p><p>你只是个普通的快递员，一次偷偷查看包裹的信件之后，更多的事情纷涌而来。</p><p>突然失踪的美人鱼在哪里？医生的秘密是什么？附近的军事测试范围真的很危险吗？疯狂的化学家在他们的实验室中做了什么？游戏暂无中文。</p><p><img src="https://hive.indienova.com/farm/article/picture/2018/9/Undelivered1.jpg" class="fr-fic fr-dib" data-id="9712" data-result="success" class="aligncenter"></p><p><img src="https://hive.indienova.com/farm/article/picture/2018/9/Undelivered2.jpg" class="fr-fic fr-dib" data-id="9713" data-result="success" class="aligncenter"></p><p class="hidden-xs"><iframe src="https://store.steampowered.com/widget/885210/" frameborder="0" style="width: 100%; height: 220px;"></iframe><br></p><h4>ZeroRanger</h4><p>关键词：清版射击</p><p>发售日期：9月29日</p><p><img src="https://hive.indienova.com/farm/article/picture/2018/9/ZeroRangerall1.jpg" class="fr-fic fr-dib" data-id="9716" data-result="success" class="aligncenter"></p><p><img src="https://hive.indienova.com/farm/article/picture/2018/9/ZeroRangerall2.jpg" class="fr-fic fr-dib" data-id="9717" data-result="success" class="aligncenter"></p><p class="hidden-xs"><iframe src="https://store.steampowered.com/widget/809020/" frameborder="0" style="width: 100%; height: 220px;"></iframe><br></p><h4>魔塔猎人 Tower Hunter:Erza's Trial</h4><p>关键词：RPG、动作、roguelike</p><p>发售日期：9月28日</p><p>一款日系画风的 roguelike+类银河战士恶魔城作品。主角 Erza 在幼年时与魔王建立了契约，在死亡时能够轮回重生。她也因此能在魔塔中不断学习与变强，成为一名出色的猎人。</p><p><img src="https://hive.indienova.com/farm/article/picture/2018/9/Tower Hunter1 mini.gif" class="fr-fic fr-dib" data-id="9675" data-result="success" class="aligncenter"></p><p><img src="https://hive.indienova.com/farm/article/picture/2018/9/Tower Hunter2.jpg" class="fr-fic fr-dib" data-id="9676" data-result="success" class="aligncenter"></p><p><img src="https://hive.indienova.com/farm/article/picture/2018/9/Tower Hunter3.jpg" class="fr-fic fr-dib" data-id="9677" data-result="success" class="aligncenter"></p><p class="hidden-xs"><iframe src="https://store.steampowered.com/widget/844850/" frameborder="0" style="width: 100%; height: 220px;"></iframe></p><h4>I’m not a Monster</h4><p>关键词：策略、多人在线、狼人杀</p><p>发售日期：9月27日</p><p>在星际飞船中潜入了可以伪装成人类的怪物，勇敢的乘客们决定站出来与怪物战斗。但是又如何区分人与怪物呢？游戏为多人在线回合制策略战，最多6名玩家，将被随机分为两个不同阵营。游戏支持中文。</p><p><img src="https://hive.indienova.com/farm/article/picture/2018/9/I’m not a Monster1.jpg" class="fr-fic fr-dib" data-id="9690" data-result="success" class="aligncenter"></p><p><img src="https://hive.indienova.com/farm/article/picture/2018/9/I’m not a Monster2.jpg" class="fr-fic fr-dib" data-id="9691" data-result="success" class="aligncenter"></p><p class="hidden-xs"><iframe src="https://store.steampowered.com/widget/826600/" frameborder="0" style="width: 100%; height: 220px;"></iframe><br></p><h4>中国式家长 / Chinese Parents</h4><p>关键词：模拟、养成</p><p>发售日期：9月29日</p><p>扮演一个普通中式家庭的孩子，再从出生到高考来一遍吧！</p><p><img src="https://hive.indienova.com/farm/article/picture/2018/9/Chinese Parents1.jpg" class="fr-fic fr-dib" data-id="9720" data-result="success" class="aligncenter"></p><p><img src="https://hive.indienova.com/farm/article/picture/2018/9/Chinese Parents2.jpg" class="fr-fic fr-dib" data-id="9721" data-result="success" class="aligncenter"></p><p><img src="https://hive.indienova.com/farm/article/picture/2018/9/Chinese Parents3.jpg" class="fr-fic fr-dib" data-id="9722" data-result="success" class="aligncenter"></p><p class="hidden-xs"><iframe src="https://store.steampowered.com/widget/736190/" frameborder="0" style="width: 100%; height: 220px;"></iframe><br></p><h4>morphe</h4><p>关键词：氛围、休闲、音乐</p><p>发售日期：9月30日</p><p>探索世界，激活方尖碑上200多种不同的音色，制作你自己的音乐。让这款游戏成为一个不错的音乐可视化软件吧。</p><p><img src="https://hive.indienova.com/farm/article/picture/2018/9/morphe1.jpg" class="fr-fic fr-dib" data-id="9718" data-result="success" class="aligncenter"></p><p><img src="https://hive.indienova.com/farm/article/picture/2018/9/morphe2.jpg" class="fr-fic fr-dib" data-id="9719" data-result="success" class="aligncenter"></p><p class="hidden-xs"><iframe src="https://store.steampowered.com/widget/931830/" frameborder="0" style="width: 100%; height: 220px;"></iframe><br></p>
